      <title>特朗普贸易缓和后的第一周全球股市意外上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-spurs-surprise-world-rally-in-first-week-on-trade-respite</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正如宣传的那样，特朗普政府执政的第一周，金融市场充满了兴奋 — — 但不是大多数投资者预期的那种兴奋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/trump-spurs-surprise-world-rally-in-first-week-on-trade-respite</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:50:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
